<div class="sourceCode" id="cb1"><pre class="sourceCode bash"><code class="sourceCode bash"><a class="sourceLine" id="cb1-1" title="1">$ <span class="ex">hexo</span> new <span class="st">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></a></code></pre></div>
